RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_RECEIVER.CONTRACT_REF_NO = OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_ENTITIES.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_RECEIVER.DIARY_EVENT_SEQ_NO = OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_ENTITIES.DIARY_EVENT_SEQ_NO AND OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_RECEIVER.RECEIVER = OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_ENTITIES.RECEIVER AND OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_RECEIVER.DIARY_EVENT_SUB_SEQ_NO = OLTMS_DIARY_MSG_ENTITIES.DIARY_EVENT_SUB_SEQ_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.USER_REF_NO, B.SHORT_NAME, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1, A.MODULE_CODE FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.COUNTERPARTY = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE IN ('OL','LP','LB','FC') AND A.BRANCH=GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH ORDER BY A.CONTRACT_REF_NO
SELECT TEMPLATE_ID, TEMPLATE_DESC FROM OLTBS_TEMPLATE_DIARY WHERE BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH

SELECT A.EVENT, A.EVENT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_DIARY_EVENT_DEFN A, LFTMS_PRODUCT_DIARY_EVENT B WHERE B.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND A.EVENT = B.EVENT_CODE AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND MODULE = A.MODULE)
SELECT CUSTOMER_NO, SHORT_NAME, CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT B.ENTITY, B.ENTITY_NAME, B.ENTITY_TYPE FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS B WHERE CUSTOMER_NO = ?
SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_DIARY_EVENT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND B.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO

RAD_SUMMARY.TITLE: LBL_CONDRYSUMMARY
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: sypks_utils.get_branch(CONTRACT_REF_NO) = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: sypks_utils.get_branch(CONTRACT_REF_NO) IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID) and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
